00:16:42.000 --> 00:16:43.040
Apa yang terjadi, Bu?

00:16:44.280 --> 00:16:45.360
Maukah kamu menghitamkan wajahku?

00:16:45.680 --> 00:16:46.880
Melarikan diri.

00:16:48.920 --> 00:16:50.680
Tuhan Krishna.

00:16:50.760 --> 00:16:53.720
